body_html:
Problem solved.

There was an environment issue, tensorflow was running in its own environment and not at base, at anaconda. A friend reinstalled a few packages at the base environment and deleted the tensorflow environmnet. I can't really say what he did, we had several trials before figuring out the problem and what to do.
